title: How to Paint Orc & Goblin Tribes Skin Tones | Intermediate Level | Warhammer: The Old World
description:
In this video, we'll show you how to paint three easy and distinctive Orc & Goblin Tribes skin tones for your Warhammer: The Old World army! 

We'll cover everything from a two-step Contrast method to adding a few Layer highlights that will make your models pop on the battlefield.

If you're new to painting, our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started.
